node.text: Michael Rosen recited his poem and I made the drawing to thank the health care workers over the pandemic. It was shown on the news. Such a privilege to be able to do this.The music is by Max Richter.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Charlie Mackesy on September 04, 2021. May be an illustration.

node.text: Hello. It’s book leaving day. I hope you’re getting on ok.

node.text: Hello. Another little distant clip I took of the boy and the mole. Not quite finished and still no sound, but getting there slowly. Thank you for being on the journey.
